OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774991532
OL,3,CMortgage rates set to keep rising,
OL,4,Cwarns former NatWest chair
OL,6,FSir Howard Davies is a former senior
OL,7,FTreasury official, banker and central
OL,8,Fbanker whose career began in the
OL,9,Faftermath of the 1973 oil crisis.
OL,11,FDavies, who stood down as chairman of
OL,12,FNatWest two years ago, says unless the
OL,13,Fcurrent conflict in the Middle East
OL,14,Fends quickly - and fears about the
OL,15,Feconomic fallout ease - borrowing
OL,16,Fcosts in Britain are likely to keep
OL,17,Frising "in the short run" for both
OL,18,Fhouseholds and the government.
OL,26,@yD@HOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
