CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774991532
OL,3,CMortgage rates set to keep rising,
OL,4,Cwarns former NatWest chair
OL,6,FAccording to Moneyfacts, rates on two-
OL,7,F and five-year fixed mortgages have
OL,8,Fclimbed to close to 6% since the war
OL,9,Fbegan four weeks ago - adding around
OL,10,F#146 a month to repayments on a
OL,11,Ftypical new two-year deal.
OL,13,FMortgage rates on two-year fixes have
OL,14,Frisen by 1.01% in just four weeks -
OL,15,Falthough that is less dramatic than
OL,16,Fthe 1.81% spike following Liz Truss's
OL,17,Fmini-budget.
OL,19,FAround 1.8 million households are due
OL,20,Fto refinance their mortgages next year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774991532
OL,3,CMortgage rates set to keep rising,
OL,4,Cwarns former NatWest chair
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"The unfortunate people who are coming
OL,12,Foff a fixed rate now and for the next
OL,13,Ffew months are just going to be hit
OL,14,Fquite hard. And that's very tough -
OL,15,Fit's just bad luck on the timing,"
OL,16,FDavies said.
OL,18,F"But that's the nature of our mortgage
OL,19,Fmarket."
OL,26,@wD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
